collectors.titleDetails: (3 total Queries, 3 of them unique across 2 Connections)

queries.sql: SELECT `skjacth_skj`.`tb_learning`.`lear_namethai`, `skjacth_skj`.`tb_learning`.`lear_id`, COUNT(skjacth_personnel.tb_personnel.pers_id) AS NumAll, (GROUP_CONCAT(skjacth_personnel.tb_personnel.pers_img)) AS AllImg FROM `tb_learning` JOIN `skjacth_personnel`.`tb_personnel` ON `skjacth_skj`.`tb_learning`.`lear_id` = `skjacth_personnel`.`tb_personnel`.`pers_learning` WHERE `pers_status` = 'กำลังใช้งาน' GROUP BY `skjacth_personnel`.`tb_personnel`.`pers_learning` ORDER BY `lear_id`

SELECT (GROUP_CONCAT(skjacth_personnel.tb_personnel.pers_img)) AS AllImg, count(skjacth_personnel.tb_personnel.pers_id) AS NumAll FROM `tb_personnel` WHERE `pers_status` = 'กำลังใช้งาน' AND `pers_position` <= 'posi_002'

SELECT `skjacth_skj`.`tb_position`.`posi_id`, `skjacth_skj`.`tb_position`.`posi_name`, count(skjacth_personnel.tb_personnel.pers_id) AS NumAll, (GROUP_CONCAT(skjacth_personnel.tb_personnel.pers_img)) AS AllImg FROM `tb_position` JOIN `skjacth_personnel`.`tb_personnel` ON `skjacth_skj`.`tb_position`.`posi_id` = `skjacth_personnel`.`tb_personnel`.`pers_position` WHERE `pers_status` = 'กำลังใช้งาน' AND `posi_id` >= 'posi_007' GROUP BY `skjacth_skj`.`tb_position`.`posi_id`
